<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Premium Short-Term Rentals | Lincoln & Nottingham</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0b1220;
      color: white;
    }

    header {
      height: 90vh;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505691938895-1758d7feb511') center/cover no-repeat;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    header::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.65);
    }

    header h1, header p, header button {
      z-index: 1;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 52px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    header p {
      max-width: 700px;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .btn {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 14px 26px;
      background: #38bdf8;
      color: black;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    section {
      padding: 70px 20px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #111b2e;
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 180px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .card-content {
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .badge {
      color: #38bdf8;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .logos {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 40px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      opacity: 0.9;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #38bdf8;
    }

    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat {
      background: #111b2e;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .testimonial {
      background: #111b2e;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      background: #0f1b33;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    input, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Premium Short-Term Rentals</h1>
  <p>We manage high-performing serviced accommodation and short-term rentals across Lincoln & Nottingham, delivering stress-free income for landlords with professional guest management and premium stays.</p>
  <a class="btn" href="#contact">Partner With Us</a>
</header>

<section>
  <h2>Trusted Platforms</h2>
  <div class="logos">
    <div>Airbnb</div>
    <div>Booking.com</div>
    <div>OpenRent</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>What We Offer Landlords</h2>
  <div class="grid">

    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560518883-ce09059eeffa" />
      <div class="card-content">
        <h3>Guaranteed Rent Options</h3>
        <p>Secure predictable monthly income with structured rental agreements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c" />
      <div class="card-content">
        <h3>Full Property Management</h3>
        <p>We handle guests, pricing, communication, and day-to-day operations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505691938895-1758d7feb511" />
      <div class="card-content">
        <h3>Cleaning & Maintenance</h3>
        <p>Professional cleaning, maintenance, and hotel-grade presentation standards.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522708323590-d24dbb6b0267" />
      <div class="card-content">
        <h3>Insurance & Protection</h3>
        <p>Guest damage protection and structured property safeguarding processes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Why Landlords Work With Us</h2>
  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <h3>Higher Returns</h3>
      <p>Optimised pricing increases rental income vs traditional letting</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h3>Zero Stress</h3>
      <p>We manage everything from bookings to guest turnover</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h3>Local Focus</h3>
      <p>Specialised in Lincoln & Nottingham markets</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Client Testimonials</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="testimonial">
      "Since working with them, my property in Nottingham has been fully managed and consistently occupied."
      <br><br><strong>- Local Landlord</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial">
      "Completely hands-off experience with better returns than traditional letting."
      <br><br><strong>- Property Investor</strong>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Example Performance</h2>
  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <h3>£1,800 → £3,200</h3>
      <p>Average monthly uplift per property (short-term vs long-term let)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h3>90%+</h3>
      <p>Average occupancy rate across managed properties</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h3>24/7</h3>
      <p>Guest support and management coverage</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="cta">
  <h2>Partner With Us</h2>
  <p>Let’s turn your property in Lincoln or Nottingham into a high-performing short-term rental asset.</p>

  <form>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Name" />
    <input type="email" placeholder="Email" />
    <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Tell us about your property"></textarea>
    <button class="btn" type="submit">Send Enquiry</button>
  </form>

  <p style="margin-top:20px;"><strong>Email:</strong> your@email.com</p>
</section>

<footer>
  © 2026 Premium Short-Term Rentals | Lincoln & Nottingham
</footer>

</body>
</html>
